Hell Girl does is fine, though.

29
00:02:14,315 --> 00:02:17,719
The people that get sent to
Hell are all bad people, anyway.

30
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:19,654
Tsugumi...

31
00:02:19,654 --> 00:02:20,985
I'm done.

32
00:02:23,825 --> 00:02:25,426
Hey, Tsugu-

33
00:02:25,426 --> 00:02:26,688
Sheesh!

34
00:02:30,665 --> 00:02:31,654
Tsugumi?!

35
00:02:44,979 --> 00:02:46,180
Tsugumi!

36
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:47,916
Tsugumi!

37
00:02:47,916 --> 00:02:49,383
Tsugumi!!

38
00:02:50,818 --> 00:02:54,222
You okay, Tsugumi?

39
00:02:54,222 --> 00:02:57,292
Yuko was with Hell Girl...

40
00:02:57,292 --> 00:02:59,227
Yuko?

41
00:02:59,227 --> 00:03:01,296
Mr. Murai's...

42
00:03:01,296 --> 00:03:03,660
My senior's?!

43
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:08,662
"Kind Neighbor"

44
