50
00:03:20,574 --> 00:03:22,201
Oh...

51
00:03:29,783 --> 00:03:31,318
Father!

52
00:03:31,318 --> 00:03:34,321
Oh, you've been drinking
so much again!

53
00:03:34,321 --> 00:03:35,989
I'm sorry that he always does this.

54
00:03:35,989 --> 00:03:38,024
Nah, I don't really mind...

55
00:03:38,024 --> 00:03:39,960
I'm not gonna drink!

56
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,027
I won't drink anymore!

57
